in%20the%20bush%20for%20five%20days%20and%20seen%20popular%20African%20animals%2C%20Kibwana%20shifted%20our%20focus%20to%20the%20creatures%20people%20sometimes%20miss%20on%20a%20safari.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20animal%20sightings%20during%20the%20author's%20stay%20at%20Singita.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67605b4d279d913c37cba162%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESide-by-side%20animal%20sightings%20during%20the%20author's%20stay%20at%20Singita.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20first%20afternoon%2C%20we%20pulled%20over%20to%20watch%20a%20leopard%20tortoise%20scurry%20through%20the%20grass.%20We%20gasped%20as%20we%20spotted%20a%20martial%20eagle%20fly%20away%20with%20its%20prey.%20Kibwana%20identified%20countless%20birds%3A%20grey-breasted%20spurfowl%2C%20Coqui%20francolin%2C%20and%20superb%20starlings.%20Watching%20these%20smaller%20animals%20offered%20a%20new%20perspective%20on%20the%20Serengeti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20game%20drive%20ended%20with%20drinks%20in%20the%20bush.%20As%20the%20sun%20dipped%20below%20the%20horizon%2C%20I%20battled%20a%20mix%20of%20emotions%3A%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave%20the%20wildlife%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20heading%20back%20to%20one%20of%20the%20most%20luxurious%20properties%20I'd%20ever%20visited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20author's%20tent.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67605bab27808b3289cd5737%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20author's%20tent.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a713e335-34ec-493e-bc75-efea6687e621%5C%22%3EThe%20Sabora%20camp%20consists%20of%20