the%20traditional%20game%20drive.%20I%20spent%20a%20morning%20on%20a%20guided%20walk%20through%20the%20bush%20and%20an%20afternoon%20visiting%20the%20nearby%20community%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20additional%20costs.%20If%20my%20stay%20had%20been%20longer%2C%20I%20could've%20commissioned%20a%20hot%20air%20balloon%20ride%2C%20booked%20spa%20treatments%2C%20and%20spent%20longer%20at%20the%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20just%20what%20Singita%20offered%3B%20it%20was%20how%20they%20offered%20it.%20At%20times%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20staff%20could%20read%20my%20mind.%20Shafuu%2C%20my%20waitress%2C%20quickly%20learned%20my%20taste%20preferences%20and%20made%20suggestions%2C%20like%20trying%20the%20fish%20fritters.%20Another%20night%2C%20the%20lodge's%20sommelier%20picked%20wine%20pairings%20for%20each%20course%20of%20my%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20passed%20by%20too%20quickly%2C%20and%20as%20I%20sat%20on%20a%20wicker%20couch%20waiting%20for%20my%20flight%20out%20of%20Sasakwa%2C%20I%20reflected%20on%20what%20made%20the%20lodge%20worth%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHearing%20lions%20roaring%20at%20night%20and%20antlers%20colliding%20in%20the%20morning%20from%20my%20king-sized%20bed%20was%20magical.%20Eating%20meals%20cooked%20with%20passion%20was%20unforgettable.%20And%20getting%20into%20the%20bush%20with%20Kibwana%20was%20thrilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20in%20such%20a%20beautiful%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Kibwana%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20makes%20this%20place%20so%20special.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20agree%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafrica-serengeti-safari-singita-sabora-tented-camp-review-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734430682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67605910279d913c37cba0c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2