0asked%20me%20to%20sell%20my%20business%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20talk%20about%20it%20until%20we%20signed%20the%20papers%20and%20closed%20because%20it%20could%20destabilize%20my%20clients%20and%20team%20if%20it%20didn't%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20sale%20was%20to%20my%20CMO.%20Even%20though%20several%20businesses%20expressed%20interest%20in%20buying%2C%20I%20preferred%20to%20sell%20to%20someone%20who%20knew%20the%20company%2C%20our%20clients%2C%20and%20how%20we%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20day%20at%209Tailors%20was%20the%20same%20day%20I%20announced%20my%20departure%20and%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20business%20to%20the%20team.%20To%20help%20transition%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20company%20for%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%2014%20years%20that%20I%20did%2C%20stayed%20on%20for%20another%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244204361-ae66-4868-8318-0ab5f7c50b60%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20work%20remotely%20for%20LookSky%2C%20as%20most%20of%20my%20team%20is%20in%20Asia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-remotely-feel-isolated-from-coworkers-quit-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorking%20remotely%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20initially%20a%20shock%20because%20I'm%20an%20extrovert%20who%20loves%20being%20around%20people%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20advantages%20is%20having%20more%20control%20over%20my%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMornings%20and%20evenings%20are%20typically%20dedicated%20to%20team%20calls.%20Afternoons%20provide%20a%20window%20for%20productive%20personal%20time%20%E2%80%94%20I%20might%20work%20out%2C%20dive%20into%20a%20business%20book%20(I'm%20reading%20%26quot%3BGood%20to%20Great%26quot%3B%20by%20James%20C.%20Collins)%2C%20or%20listen%20to%20a%20startup%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-podcasts-silicon-valley-ideology-andreessen-horowitz-calacanis-palihapitiya-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C