it%20impossible%20for%20him%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20'face'%20of%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Diageo%20lawyers%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20a%20judge%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20January%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20resolved.%20Combs%20received%20%24200%20million%20for%20his%20stake%20in%20DeLe%C3%B3n%20tequila%20and%20not%20a%20penny%20for%20his%20longtime%20work%20with%20C%C3%AEroc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20similar%20story%20for%20his%20other%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs'%20lifestyle%20company%2C%20Sean%20John%2C%20had%20already%20slipped%3A%20In%202016%2C%20he%20sold%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20the%20business%2C%20which%20at%20that%20point%20included%20fragrances%20and%20furnishings%2C%20to%20Global%20Brands%20Group%20for%20%2470%20million%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fzackomalleygreenburg%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2Fwhy-diddy-is-no-1-on-the-2017-celebrity-100-list%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Just%20five%20years%20later%2C%20Global%20Brands%20Group%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20protection%2C%20and%20Combs%20bought%20back%20the%20business%20for%20%247.55%20million%2C%20just%20over%2010%25%20of%20what%20it%20was%20once%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clothing%20line's%20website%20has%20gone%20defunct%2C%20its%20Instagram%20scrapped%2C%20and%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20sold%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmacys-covered-up-2008-flagship-store-sex-attack-diddy-lawsuit-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMacy's%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20once%20the%20exclusive%20home%20of%20the%20brand's%20sportswear%20line%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20of%20its%20last%20remaining%20retailers.%20The%20department%20store%2C%20which%20was%20accused%20by%20one%20of%20Buzbee's%20clients%20of%20covering%20up%20a%202008%20sexual%20attack%20by%20Combs%2C%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20whether%20the%20removal%20of%20his%20Sean%20John%20line%20had%20to%20do%