A0bill%20does%20not%20have%20support...%20many%20parties%20have%20spoken%20against%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20bill%20will%20likely%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20joint%20committee%20that%20will%20be%20constituted%20based%20on%20each%20party's%20Lok%20Sabha%20numbers.%20This%20will%20mean%20the%20BJP%20will%20have%20the%20maximum%20members%20and%20lead%20the%20committee%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20(129th%20Amendment)%20Bill%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20this%20afternoon%20by%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal.%20The%20introduction%20was%20followed%20by%20scathing%20attacks%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%2C%20Opposition%20Slam%20ONOP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Dharmendra%20Yadav%2C%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20and%20TR%20Baalu%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20led%20the%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20of%20ex-Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20group%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20host%20of%20smaller%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%2C%20also%20voiced%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-poll-bill-aligned-with-ease-of-elections-law-minister-7267486%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNot%20Tampering%20With%20State%20Powers%26quot%3B%3A%20Law%20Minister%20On%20'ONOP'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20thread%20among%20critics%20of%20the%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Poll'%2C%20or%20ONOP%20Bill%2C%20was%20that%20the%20simultaneous%20elections%20proposal%20subverts%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20must%20be%20withdrawn%20immediately.%20Mr%20Yadav%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20warned%20the%20House%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20path%20to%20dictatorship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Trinamool%20boss%20and%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20design%20to%20subvert%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20slammed%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-federal%26quot%3B%20exercise%2C%20labelling%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20authoritarian%20imposition%20designed%20to%20undermine%20India's%20democracy%20and%20federal%20structure%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-mamata-banerjee-must-save-indias-democracy-mamata-opposition-slam-one-nation-one-poll-7232783%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BMust%20Save%20Democracy%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Opposition%20Slam%20'1%20Nation%2C%201%20Poll'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Baalu%20flagged%20the%20expenditure%20simultaneous%20polls%20entailed%2C%20including%20the%20Election%20Commission%20having%20to%20spend%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20on%20new%20EVMs%2C%20or%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20every%2015%20years.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20should%20send%20this%20bill%20to%20the%20JPC%20(joint%20parliamentary%20committee)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-estimates-rs-10-000-crore-needed-every-15-years-for-new-evms-if-simultaneous-polls-held-4898470%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERs%2010%2C000%20Crore%20Every%2015%20Years%20-%20Cost%20Of%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Poll'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BUnwavering%20Support%26quot%3B%20From%20BJP%20Allies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20BJP's%20allies%20-%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20the%20Sena%20faction%20of%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20-%20established%20their%20backing%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(that)%20when%20simultaneous%20elections%20happen...%20there%20is%20clarity%20of%20process%20and%20governance.%20That%20has%20been%20our%20experience%20and%20we%20want%20that%20to%20happen%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TDP's%20Lavu%20Sri%20Krishna%20Devarayalu%20said%2C%20expressing%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%20support%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Responds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20to%20speak%20after%20the%20avalanche%20of%20criticism%2C%20Mr%20Meghwal%20hit%20back%20and%20insisted%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20proposal%20is%20a%20long-pending%20piece%20of%20electoral%20reform%20and%20will%20not%20damage%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaws%20can%20be%20brought%20in%20for%20electoral%20reforms...%20this%20bill%20is%20aligned%20with%20the%20process%20of%20easing%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20which%20will%20be%20synchronised.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20Constitution%20via%20this%20Bill.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20tampering%20with%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20it%20means%20all%20Indians%20will%20vote%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20-%20to%20pick%20central%20and%20state%20representatives%20-%20in%20the%20same%20year%2C%20if%20not%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%202024%2C%20only%20four%20states%20voted%20with%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20Odisha%20voted%20alongside%20the%20April-June%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.