ent%20years.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20drones%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermany-drones-spotted-over-us-air-base-in-ramstein%2Fa-71053878%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20spotted%3C%2Fa%3E%20above%20an%20American%20base%20in%20Germany.%20Some%20have%20been%20spotted%20near%20US%20operations%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20base%20in%20Virginia%2C%20among%20other%20stateside%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20levels%20vary.%20Drones%20are%20readily%20available%20to%20both%20malign%20actors%20and%20harmless%20hobbyists%20alike.%20The%20challenge%20is%20that%20it%20can%20sometimes%20be%20difficult%20to%20distinguish%20which%20it%20is%2C%20and%20drones%20lower%20the%20barrier%20for%20entry%20on%20aerial%20surveillance%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20become%20a%20huge%20problem%20for%20both%20military%20and%20civilian%20airfields%20and%20will%20get%20worse%20as%20drone%20usage%20proliferates%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20defense%20expert%20and%20retired%20US%20Marine%20Corps%20colonel%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20has%20national%20security%20implications%20as%20many%20drones%20fly%20over%20sensitive%20military%20facilities%20like%20Wright-Patterson.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20drones%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fclyvnnj8g34o%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20near%20civilian%20airports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Cancian%2C%20now%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20said%20that%20such%20activity%20could%20be%20a%20safety%20hazard%20and%20interfere%20with%20the%20flow%20of%20operations.%20This%20can%20be%20a%20huge%20disruption%20at%20a%20major%20airport%20with%20nationwide%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20recent%20East%20Coast%20drone%20drama%2C%20runway%20operations%20at%20a%20New%20York%20airport%20were%20briefly%20sh