the%20Constitution%2C%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20told%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Tuesday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaws%20can%20be%20brought%20in%20for%20electoral%20reforms...%20this%20bill%20is%20aligned%20with%20the%20process%20of%20easing%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20which%20will%20be%20synchronised.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20Constitution%20via%20this%20Bill.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20tampering%20with%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Meghwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Meghwal%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20panel%20led%20by%20ex-President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20which%20had%20been%20tasked%20with%20recommending%20ways%20to%20make%20the%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fone-nation-one-election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%3C%2Fa%3E'%20proposal%20a%20reality%2C%20had%20consulted%20multiple%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20various%20opposition%20parties%2C%20before%20submitting%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20tampering%20with%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted%2C%20after%20which%20he%20proposed%20that%20the%20bill%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20-%20as%20was%20expected%20-%20for%20wider%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20told%20NDTV%20last%20night%20the%20bill%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20JPC%2C%20and%20that%20its%20constitution%20will%20be%20finalised%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%20The%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20House%2C%20will%20hold%20the%20maximum%20seats%20and%20lead%20the%20committee.%20MPs%20will%20be%20nominated%20based%20on%20their%20parties'%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Meghwal's%20defence%2C%20a%20division%20of%20votes%20was%20demanded%20to%20introduce%20the%20'bill%2C%20to%20which%20the%20Speaker%20agreed%3B%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20held%20a%20division%20vote%20to%20table%20a%20Constitutional%20Amendment%20Bill.%20The%20Bill%20was%20introduced%20after%20269%20MPs%20voted%20in%20favour%20and%20198%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Minister's%20response%20followed%20a%20furious%20pushback%20from%20the%20opposition%20after%20the%20bill%20-%20which%20seeks%20to%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20to%20permit%20simultaneous%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20-%20was%20tabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20(129th%20Amendment)%20Bill%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-bill-lok-sabha-one-nation-one-election-bill-likely-in-lok-sabha-to-be-sent-to-committee-7262461%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll_Imagetopscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswiftly%20slammed%20as%20%26quot%3Bbeyond%20the%20House's%20legislative%20competence%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20path%20to%20dictatorship%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20federal%20nature%20of%20the%20Indian%20republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20began%20in%20the%20post-noon%20session%20after%20Mr%20Meghwal%20tabled%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%2C%20SP%20Lead%20ONOP%20Pushback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20Chandigarh%20MP%2C%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20led%20the%20opposition's%20charge%2C%20denouncing%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20flagship%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20poll'%20push%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20Constitution%20-%20on%20which%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20held%20a%20bitterly-charged%20and%20vociferous%20debate%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArticle%201%20of%20the%20Constitution%20says%20'...%20India%2C%20that%20is%20Bharat%2C%20shall%20be%20a%20Union%20of%20States%2C%20affirming%20its%20federal%20character'.%20This%20bill%2C%20which%20proposes%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20directly%20challenges%20this%20framework%20by%20imposing%20uniformity%20across%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tewari%20said%2C%20outlining%20the%20first%20of%20his%20party's%20three%20objections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-poll-bjp-vs-opposition-on-one-nation-one-poll-ahead-of-parliament-storm-7267007%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20vs%20Opposition%20On%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Poll'%20Ahead%20Of%20Parliament%20Storm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20argued%20simultaneous%20polls%20would%20impact%20the%20Constitution's%20basic%20structure%20and%20%26quot%3Bundermine%20elected%20state%20governments%2C%20weaken%20grassroots%20democracy%2C%20and%20encroach%20on%20local%20governance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Dharmendra%20Yadav%2C%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20and%20TR%20Baalu%20of%20the%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20followed%2C%20and%20each%20was%20sharply%20critical.%20Mr%20Yadav%20warned%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20path%20to%20dictatorship%26quot%3B%20and%20Mr%20Banerjee%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bhits%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Baalu%20flagged%20the%20expenditure%20simultaneous%20polls%20entailed%2C%20including%20the%20Election%20Commission%20having%20to%20spend%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20on%20new%20EVMs%2C%20or%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20every%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-estimates-rs-10-000-crore-needed-every-15-years-for-new-evms-if-simultaneous-polls-held-4898470%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERs%2010%2C000%20Crore%20Every%2015%20Years%20-%20Cost%20Of%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Poll'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20should%20send%20this%20bill%20to%20the%20JPC%20(joint%20parliamentary%20committee).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EShiv%20Sena%2C%20NCP%2C%20Owaisi%20Join%20Protest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20group%20led%20by%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20its%20state%20ally%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20both%20also%20expressed%20their%20opposition.%20The%20Sena%20(UBT)%20called%20the%20bill%20%26quot%3Ban%20attack%20on%20federalism%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20Ms%20Sule%20echoed%20earlier%20points%20of%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsaduddin%20Owaisi%20of%20the%20AIMIM%20rose%20to%20make%20a%20brief%20but%20forceful%20point%2C%20asserting%20the%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20Constitution%20would%20violate%20states'%20right%20to%20self-governance.%20Mr%20Owaisi%20also%20argued%2C%20as%20other%20opposition%20leaders%20have%2C%20that%20simultaneous%20elections%20will%20spell%20the%20end%20of%20regional%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2C%20however%2C%20also%20stray%20voices%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BUnwavering%20Support%26quot%3B%20From%20BJP%20Allies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20BJP's%20allies%20-%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20the%20Sena%20faction%20of%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20-%20established%20their%20backing%20of%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(that)%20when%20simultaneous%20elections%20happen...%20there%20is%20clarity%20of%20process%20and%20governance.%20That%20has%20been%20our%20experience%20and%20we%20want%20that%20to%20happen%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20TDP's%20Lavu%20Sri%20Krishna%20Devarayalu%20said%2C%20expressing%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%20support%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20has%2016%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%2C%20which%2C%20combined%20with%20the%2012%20of%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%2C%20was%20critical%20in%20allowing%20the%20BJP%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%20April-June%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20one%20of%20four%20states%20to%20hold%20Assembly%20elections%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20this%20year%2C%20as%20voting%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20other%20three%20were%20Sikkim%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20it%20means%20all%20Indians%20will%20vote%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20-%20to%20pick%20central%20and%20state%20representatives%20-%20in%20the%20same%20year%2C%20if%20not%20at%20the%20same%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%202024%2C%20only%20four%20states%20voted%20with%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20Odisha%20voted%20alongside%20the%20April-June%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Three%20others%20-%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20-%20voted%20in%20October-November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Special%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-explained-what-is-it-how-will-it-work-6602206%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%3A%20What%20Is%20It%20And%20How%20Will%20It%20Work%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20follow%20a%20non-synced%20five-year%20cycle%3B%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Telangana%2C%20for%20example%2C%20were%20among%20those%20voted%20at%20different%20times%20last%20year%2C%20while%20Delhi%20and%20Bihar%20will%20vote%20in%202025%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Bengal%20are%20among%20those%20that%20will%20vote%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20Work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20without%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%20and%20that%20amendment%20being%20ratified%20by%20the%20governments%20of%20all%20states%20and%20union%20territories%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20possibly%2C%20major%20political%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-one-nation-one-election-means-and-why-its-being-done-4347498%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'.%20What%20Are%20Pros%20And%20Cons%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20Article%2083%20(term%20of%20Parliament)%2C%20Article%2085%20(dissolution%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20the%20President)%2C%20Article%20172%20(duration%20of%20state%20legislatures)%2C%20and%20Article%20174%20(dissolution%20of%20state%20legislatures)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Article%20356%20(imposition%20of%20President's%20Rule).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20experts%20have%20warned%20that%20failure%20to%20pass%20such%20amendments%20will%20leave%20the%20proposal%20open%20to%20attack%20on%20charges%20of%20violating%20India's%20federal%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734424740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fq0k9v5r_arjun-ram-meghwal-one-nation-one-poll-bill_625x300_17_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-poll-bill-aligned-with-ease-of-elections-law-minister-7267486%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20proposal%20to%20hold%20simultaneous%20federal%20and%20state%20elections%20-%20the%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20poll'%20proposal%20-%20is%20a%20long-pending%20piece%20of%20electoral