rming%20in%20challenging%20conditions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20grew%20up%20immersed%20in%20the%20rhythms%20of%20rural%20life.%20Agriculture%20became%20his%20way%20of%20honouring%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20wanted%20to%20follow%20in%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20to%20carry%20on%20the%20family%20tradition%2C%20but%20to%20support%20him%20in%20his%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20earning%20a%20diploma%20in%20agriculture%2C%20his%20path%20became%20clear.%20He%20pursued%20the%20course%20to%20enhance%20his%20skills%20and%20deepen%20his%20understanding%20of%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turning%20point%20came%20when%20he%20started%20considering%20the%20future%20of%20agriculture%20in%20his%20region.%20He%20realised%20that%20to%20make%20a%20meaningful%20impact%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20innovate%20and%20focus%20on%20sustainable%20crops%20that%20could%20thrive%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20challenging%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-03-at-19.42.31-1_11zon-1734345976-500x889.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parmeshwar%20Thorat%20started%20his%20journey%20by%20planting%2050%20avocado%20saplings%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-03-at-19.42.31-1_11zon-1734345976-500x889.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-03-at-19.42.31-1_11zon-1734345976-169x300.jpeg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-03-at-19.42.31-1_11zon-1734345976-768x1366.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-