%2C%20he%20ordered%2050%20avocado%20saplings%20from%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20starting%20avocado%20farming%20in%20Beed%20was%20far%20from%20easy.%20The%20region%20being%20notorious%20for%20its%20extreme%20temperatures%20and%20chronic%20water%20scarcity%2C%20the%20challenges%20initially%20seemed%20insurmountable%20for%20cultivating%20avocados.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20very%20little%20knowledge%20about%20avocado%20farming%20here%2C%20and%20no%20one%20had%20attempted%20it%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmeshwar%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20overcome%20these%20challenges%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20dig%20two%20feet%20by%20two%20feet%20pits%20across%200.75%20acres%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20filled%20them%20with%20cow%20dung%20manure%20before%20planting%20the%20saplings.%20I%20knew%20the%20soil%20needed%20enrichment%20to%20supply%20the%20nutrients%20the%20plants%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system%20to%20ensure%20the%20saplings%20received%20adequate%20water%20without%20wastage.%20%E2%80%9CDrip%20irrigation%20takes%20water%20and%20other%20nutrients%20directly%20to%20the%20roots%2C%20minimising%20wastage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%20also%20utilised%20a%20pond%20on%20his%20farm%20to%20capture%20rainwater%20runoff.%20The%20stored%20water%20is%20used%20during%20the%20dry%20months%20of%20March%20and%20April%2C%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20groundwater.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20collect%20as%20much%20rainwater%20as%20possible%20during%20the%20monsoon%20and%20use%20it%20during%20the%20dry%20seasons.%20It%20helps%20keep%20the%20farm%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20careful%20planning%20bore%20fruit%20when%20the%20first%20avocados%20were%20harvested%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20doubt%20to%20demand%3A%20Building%20a%20market%20for%20avocados%3C%