n%20crew%20member%20and%20the%20passenger%20were%20intercepted%20by%20the%20officials%20when%20they%20arrived%20at%20Chennai%20on%20an%20Air%20India%20Flight%20from%20Dubai%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20passenger%20admitted%20to%20handing%20over%20the%20gold%20to%20the%20cabin%20crew%20member%20inside%20the%20flight%2C%20%C2%A0the%20customs%20department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20search%20resulted%20in%20the%20recovery%20of%20gold%20in%20compound%20form%2C%20concealed%20in%20the%20undergarments%20of%20the%20cabin%20crew%2C%26quot%3B%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20have%20been%20remanded%20under%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734424020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fi5eo6nsg_chennai-drugs_625x300_17_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fchennai-news%2Fkenya-woman-ingests-cocaine-capsules-worth-14-crore-arrested-at-chennai-airport-7267704%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai%3A%20A%20Kenyan%20woman%20who%20ingested%2090%20capsules%20containing%20cocaine%20worth%20Rs%2014.2%20crore%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20customs%20officials%20at%20the%20Chennai%20Airport%2C%20authorities%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fchennai-news%2Fkenya-woman-ingests-cocaine-capsules-worth-14-crore-arrested-at-chennai-airport-7267704%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Like%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20too%2C%20a%20master%20of%20his%20own%20demise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734423999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116394494%2Cimgsize-32208.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-australia%2Flike-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-too-a-maste