ll%20have%20to%20keep%20making%20way%20for%20T20s%2C%20just%20like%20One-Day%20cricket%20has%20had%20to%20do%3F%20Or%20has%20that%20already%20happened%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%2023%20bilateral%20men's%20Test%20series%20being%20played%20in%202024%2C%20as%20many%20as%2012%20had%20only%20two%20matches%2C%20five%20had%20three%20matches%20and%20only%20two%20had%20five%20matches%20(England%20in%20India%20and%20India%20in%20Australia).%20Let's%20make%20no%20mistake%E2%80%94we%20are%20currently%20living%20in%20a%20time%20that%20is%20witnessing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20dichotomies%20in%20cricket%20viewership%20patterns.%20While%20the%20real%20fan%20demand%20seems%20to%20have%20well%20and%20truly%20shifted%20to%20T20%20cricket%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20time%20when%20a%20day-night%20Test%20in%20Adelaide%20between%20Australia%20and%20India%20sees%20six%20of%20the%20seven%20sessions%20of%20play%20more%20than%20one%20million%20viewers%20on%20average%2C%20across%20all%20platforms.%20The%20first%20two%20days%20of%20the%20Perth%20Test%20between%20Australia%20and%20India%20saw%20a%20record%20number%20of%20people%20go%20through%20the%20stadium%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Test%20In%20Patience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20it's%20called%20'Test'%20cricket%20because%20it%20tests%20the%20players%20involved%20and%20their%20skill%20sets.%20What%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20the%20game%20also%20tests%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20patience%20of%20the%20viewers.%20There's%20a%20certain%20time%20commitment%20that%20Test%20cricket%20demands%2C%20and%2C%20let's%20face%20it%2C%20time%20is%20what%20most%20people%20don't%20have%20in%20today's%20day%20and%20age.%20It's%20true%20that%20purists%20who%20prefer%20a%20clash%20in%20all%20whites%20still%20live%20and%20breathe%2C%20but%20they%20make%20up%20a%20very%20small%20pool.%20Many%20Indian%20fans%20are%20also%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20in%20Australia%2C%20but%20how%20many%20of%20them%20will%20also%20be%20watching%20the%20England%20vs%20New%20Zealand%20series%3F%20How%20many%20of%20them%20will%20tune%20in%20to%20watch%20Pakistan%20take%20on%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20longest%20format%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherein%20lies%20the%20real%20problem.%20Many%20fans%20still%20like%20to%20watch%20Test%20cricket%20when%20their%20own%20country%20is%20in%20action%20no%20doubt%2C%20but%20not%20otherwise.%20How%20many%20Indian%20fans%2C%20for%20example%2C%20will%20get%20up%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20catch%20a%20day%20of%20Ashes%20cricket%20in%20Australia%3F%20Compare%20that%20to%20T20%20cricket%2C%20made%20almost%20invincible%20with%20its%20enviable%20franchise%20formula%2C%20and%20you%20will%20see%20there%20is%20a%20rather%20large%20gulf%20that%20has%20formed.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Alistair%20Dobson%2C%20the%20General%20Manager%20of%20the%20Big%20Bash%20leagues%20(men%20and%20women)%20in%20Australia%20talked%20about%20%E2%80%9Ca%20significant%20increase%20in%20audiences%20globally%20this%20year%2C%20particularly%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Big%20Bash%2C%20Australia's%20franchise%20T20%20competition%2C%20even%20added%20Indian%20commentators%20like%20Ravi%20Shastri%20and%20Harsha%20Bhogle%20to%20their%20broadcast%20roster%20to%20woo%20larger%20Indian%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorrying%20Signs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20cricketers%20themselves%20who%20are%20choosing%20the%20shortest%20format%20over%20Tests.%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20chose%20to%20retire%20from%20Test%20cricket%20aged%2029%20and%20from%20ODIs%20at%20the%20age%20of%2031%20to%20focus%20on%20T20%20cricket.%20Kane%20Williamson%20(32%20Test%20centuries)%20stunned%20the%20cricketing%20world%20when%20he%20stepped%20down%20as%20Kiwi%20white-ball%20captain%2C%20not%20accepting%20a%20central%20contract%20for%20the%202024-25%20season.%20He%20also%20announced%20his%20aim%20to%20play%20in%20the%20SA20%E2%80%94South%20Africa's%20franchise-based%20T20%20tournament.%20Cricket%20South%20Africa%20had%20to%20send%20a%20considerably%20weakened%20team%20for%20their%20two-Test%20tour%20of%20New%20Zealand%20earlier%20this%20year%20(and%20lost%200-2)%20because%20the%20dates%20clashed%20with%20the%20SA20.%20These%20are%20worrying%20signs%20for%20the%20overall%20health%20of%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20viewers%20would%20also%20argue%20that%20Tests%20just%20don't%20give%20them%20the%20adrenaline%20rush%20that%20T20s%20do.%20But%20a%20look%20back%20at%202024%20shows%20just%20how%20nail-biting%20and%20exciting%20men's%20Test%20cricket%20has%20been.%20Before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20third%20Australia%20vs%20India%20Test%20in%20Brisbane%20and%20the%20third%20New%20Zealand%20vs%20England%20Test%20in%20Hamilton%2C%20there%20have%20been%2048%20Tests%20played%20this%20year%20and%20incredibly%2C%20only%20one%20of%20them%20(WI%20vs%20SA%20in%20Port%20of%20Spain%20in%20August)%20ended%20in%20a%20draw.%20This%20was%20a%20year%20that%20saw%20India%20beat%20South%20Africa%20in%20Cape%20Town%2C%20with%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20taking%2012%20wickets%20in%20the%20match.%20This%20was%20only%20the%20second%20time%20the%20Proteas%20lost%20a%20Test%20at%20this%20venue%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20India's%20first%20ever%20Test%20win%20in%20Cape%20Town.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20year%20that%20saw%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20currently%20ranked%208th%20in%20the%20ICC%20rankings%2C%20beat%20Australia%20in%20Brisbane%20in%20the%20day-night%20Test%20in%20January%20by%20eight%20runs.%20England%20beat%20India%20in%20Hyderabad%20by%2028%20runs.%20Bangladesh%20beat%20Pakistan%20in%20Rawalpindi%20and%20New%20Zealand%20whitewashed%20India%203-0%20in%20India.%20These%20were%20all%20hugely%20entertaining%20matches%2C%20replete%20with%20suspense%20and%20drama.%20But%2C%20just%20how%20big%20an%20impact%20will%20these%20have%20on%20the%20overall%20interest%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20globally%3F%20If%20you%20haven't%20watched%20a%20non-India%20Test%20match%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20will%20these%20results%20make%20you%20watch%20other%20teams%20in%20action%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdd%20Some%20Drama%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20factor%20that%20works%20against%20Test%20cricket%20becoming%20more%20exciting%20is%20the%20deep%20gulf%20between%20the%20%E2%80%98top%20teams'%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98middling'%20ones%E2%80%94which%20do%20beat%20the%20top%20teams%20once%20in%20a%20while%E2%80%94and%20the%20%E2%80%98minnows'.%20While%20teams%20like%20Australia%2C%20India%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20England%20and%20New%20Zealand%20are%20the%20alphas%20of%20the%20pack%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20West%20Indies%20and%20Bangladesh%20are%20dark%20horses%2C%20capable%20of%20pulling%20off%20upsets%20against%20the%20%E2%80%98big%20boys'%2C%20but%20more%20often%20than%20not%20likely%20to%20lose%20to%20them.%20And%20then%20there%20are%20the%20likes%20of%20Ireland%2C%20Zimbabwe%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20who%20bring%20up%20the%20rear%20of%20the%2012-team%20rankings.%20The%20cricket%20economy%2C%20driven%20mostly%20by%20broadcast%20rights%2C%20doesn't%20allow%20big%20teams%20to%20play%20bilaterals%20against%20the%20%E2%80%98minnows'%20too%20often.%20Australia%20beating%20India%20or%20the%20other%20way%20around%20might%20be%20exciting%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20really%20result%20in%20any%20serious%20jaw-dropping.%20Many%20a%20jaw%20would%20drop%20though%20if%20Afghanistan%20beat%20England%20or%20Ireland%20crushed%20New%20Zealand.%20And%20that%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20format's%20popularity%20too%2C%20because%20the%20one%20thing%20neutral%20fans%20want%20to%20see%20more%20than%20anything%20else%20is%20exciting%2C%20unpredictable%20cricket.%20When%20Afghanistan%20beat%20Australia%20to%20reach%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20it%20did%20wonders%20for%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20format.%20The%20same%20happened%20when%20Ireland%20beat%20England%20(DLS%20method)%20in%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Test%20cricket%20could%20also%20do%20with%20a%20similar%20adrenaline%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFranchise%20cricket%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20taken%20a%20cricketer's%20workload%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level.%20Scheduling%20bilateral%20series%20and%20trying%20to%20squeeze%20in%20a%20respectable%20number%20of%20Tests%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20difficult.%20One%20suggestion%20that%20has%20been%20made%20by%20some%20like%20Ravi%20Shastri%20and%20Michael%20Vaughan%20is%20to%20have%20two%20tiers%20of%20Test%20cricket%E2%80%94a%20Top%206%20and%20a%20Bottom%206%2C%20with%20teams%20mostly%20playing%20other%20teams%20in%20the%20same%20tier.%20Vaughan%20has%20also%20suggested%20reducing%20Test%20cricket%20to%20four-day%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChange%20is%20the%20only%20constant.%20The%20governing%20bodies%20of%20cricket%20need%20to%20change%20with%20the%20times%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20evolution%20that%20we%20are%20seeing%20in%20fans'%20preferences.%20The%20future%20looks%20exciting%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20various%20different%20blueprints%20that%20can%20be%20drawn%20up.%20Let's%20just%20hope%20that%20the%20soul%20of%20Test%20cricket%20is%20not%20tampered%20with%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734423420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fekv7pfqo_india-afp_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcan-test-cricket-stand-the-test-of-time-and-the-lure-of-t20s-7267780%