my%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20that%20a%20temporary%20flight%20restriction%20had%20been%20enacted%20over%20Picatinny%20Arsenal%2C%20effective%20until%20December%2026%2C%20following%20the%20recent%20spate%20of%20drone%20activity.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20sightings%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20(FAA)%20is%20also%20investigating%2C%20and%20additional%20flight%20restrictions%20have%20been%20imposed%20over%20nearby%20areas%2C%20including%20the%20Trump%20National%20Golf%20Club%20in%20Bedminster.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20mystery%20surrounding%20the%20drones%20has%20sparked%20public%20concern.%20New%20Jersey%20State%20Senator%20Joe%20Pennacchio%20recently%20called%20for%20a%20federal%20investigation%20and%20even%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20expressing%20frustration%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20answers.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDespite%20regulations%20designed%20to%20prevent%20drones%20from%20flying%20into%20restricted%20zones%2C%20experts%20suggest%20that%20some%20drones%20may%20have%20been%20tampered%20with%20or%20hacked%20to%20bypass%20such%20restrictions.%20A%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20federal%20authorities%20filed%20charges%20against%20a%20Chinese%20national%20for%20using%20a%20modified%20drone%20to%20take%20photos%20of%20Vandenberg%20Space%20Force%20Base%2C%20raising%20further%20concerns%20about%20drone%20security.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnEven%20as%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20drones%20over%20New%20Jersey%20remain%20a%20mystery%2C%20John%20Kirby%2C%20White%20House%20national%20security%20communications%20adviser%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUpon%20review%20of%20available%20imagery%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20many%20of%20the%20reported%20sightings%20are%20manned%20aircraft%20that%20are%20being%20operated%20lawfully.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmid%20all%20this%2C%20Laura%20Ballman%2C%20a%20former%20CIA%20operations%20officer%2C%20speculated%20on%20Fox%20News%20Live%20that%20the%20unidentified%20drones%20might%20be%2