plit%20the%20former%20Raj%20province%20of%20Punjab%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20website%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20the%20usage%20of%20the%20word%20'Panjab'%20has%20often%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20entire%20region%20as%20one%20state%20before%20the%20partition%20of%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20background%2C%20the%20post%20by%20Dhillon%20becomes%20significant%20as%20she%20would%20take%20up%20the%20post%20as%20the%20Assistant%20Attorney%20General%20for%20Civil%20Rights%20at%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20under%20the%20upcoming%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Civil%20Rights%20Division%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20major%20civil%20rights%20issues%20of%20the%20US%20and%20also%20has%20prominence%20in%20key%20international%20issues%20as%20it%20is%20involved%20directly%20in%20addressing%20issues%20such%20as%20justice%20for%20victims%20of%20overseas%20terrorism%2C%20organised%20crime%20and%20cyber%20security%20amongst%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%20announcing%20her%20nomination%2C%20Trump%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20pleased%20to%20nominate%20Harmeet%20K.%20Dhillon%20as%20Assistant%20Attorney%20General%20for%20Civil%20Rights%20at%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20her%20career%2C%20Harmeet%20has%20stood%20up%20consistently%20to%20protect%20our%20cherished%20Civil%20Liberties%2C%20including%20taking%20on%20Big%20Tech%20for%20censoring%20our%20Free%20Speech...Harmeet%20is%20a%20respected%20member%20of%20the%20Sikh%20religious%20community.%20In%20her%20new%20role%20at%20the%20DOJ%2C%20Harmeet%20will%20be%20a%20tireless%20defender%20of%20our%20Constitutional%20Rights%2C%20and%20will%20enforce%20our%20Civil%20Rights%20and%20Election%20Laws%20FAIRLY%20and%20FIRMLY.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%