%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-hush-money-sentencing-postponed-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20sentencing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20been%20delayed%20three%20times%20and%20currently%20remains%20without%20a%20scheduled%20date%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20unclear.%20Prosecutors%20have%20urged%20that%20the%20conviction%20stand%2C%20even%20if%20that%20means%20Trump%20is%20sentenced%20after%20his%20second%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-judge-juan-merchan-manhattan-mental-health-court-wednesday-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustice%20Juan%20Merchan%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20sentencing%20in%20Monday's%20strongly%20worded%2C%2042-page%20rebuff%2C%20which%20was%20centered%20on%20presidential%20immunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-immunity-no-bearing-hush-money-conviction-da-bragg-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresidential%20immunity%20does%20not%20apply%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20hush-money%20case%20because%20the%20case%20hinged%20on%20%26quot%3Bdecidedly%20personal%20acts%2C%26quot%3B%20Merchan%20found%2C%20agreeing%20with%20arguments%20by%20Manhattan%20District%20Attorney%20Alvin%20Bragg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20Court%20was%20careful%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20'The%20President%2C%20charged%20with%20enforcing%20federal%20criminal%20laws%2C%20is%20not%20above%20them%2C'%26quot%3B%20Merchan%20wrote%2C%20quoting%20from%20the%20landmark%20June%20SCOTUS%20decision%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-trump-immunity-january-6-election-ruling-decision-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egranting%20presidents%20broad%20immunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Trump%20have%20repeatedly%20challenged%20the%20case%20on%20presidential%20immunity%20gr