ans.%20We%20provide%20banana%20fibre%20and%20bark%20as%20eco-friendly%20fillers%20for%20packaging.%20We%20also%20use%20these%20materials%20to%20package%20our%20own%20handicrafts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20product%20is%20delivered%2C%20customers%20can%20repurpose%20the%20fibre%20from%20the%20packaging%20in%20their%20gardens%2C%20as%20it%20provides%20valuable%20nutrients%20for%20plants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunway%20India%20has%20also%20explored%20creating%20paper%20from%20banana%20stem%20mulch.%20This%20paper%20is%20used%20for%20wrapping%20handicrafts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20crafting%20greeting%20cards%20and%20flower%20bouquets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fo1Jdi9AQA4A%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraining%20and%20capacity%20building%20are%20central%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20The%20enterprise%20has%20partnered%20with%20Assam%20Rifles%20to%20provide%20training%20to%20women%20in%20areas%20affected%20by%20poverty%20and%20insurgency.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20conducts%20workshops%20in%20schools%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(2020)%20skill%20development%20module.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Light%2C%20sturdy%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountry%20boats%20are%20prone%20to%20leaks%20and%20instability%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20fatal%20accidents%20each%20year.%20While%20fibre-glass%20boats%20are%20a%20common%20alternative%2C%20they%20are%20neither%20biodegradable%20nor%20recyclable%2C%20often%20ending%20up%