proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Deka%20at%20work%20designing%20the%20boats%20(L)%3B%20A%20canoe%20made%20of%20bamboo%20composites%20(R)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-10-1733827742-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388179%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERavi%20Deka%20at%20work%20designing%20the%20boats%20(L)%3B%20A%20canoe%20made%20of%20bamboo%20composites%20(R)%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Akvotransiro%20Tech%20Pvt%20Ltd%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boats%20are%2040%20to%2060%20percent%20lighter%20than%20their%20fibre-glass%20or%20wooden%20counterparts.%20With%20bamboo%20boats%2C%20you%20can%20achieve%20good%20speeds%20using%20less%20power%2C%20making%20them%20more%20efficient%20and%20lowering%20running%20costs%2C%20he%20further%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20incubated%20at%20IIT%20Guwahati%20and%20has%20developed%20prototypes%20of%20six%20different%20types%20of%20bamboo%20composite%20boats%2C%20with%20patents%20pending.%20The%20smallest%20boat%20is%20a%20three-person%20canoe%2C%20while%20the%20company%2