%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVibrant%20dance%20performances%20light%20up%20the%20Sume%20Gelirak%20Festival%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Travel%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20festival%20is%20filled%20with%20joyful%20music%20and%20dance%20performances%2C%20which%20express%20the%20tribe%E2%80%99s%20happiness%20and%20respect%20for%20their%20gods.%20Rituals%20are%20performed%20to%20honour%20these%20deities%2C%20keeping%20ancient%20traditions%20alive.%20The%20festival%20offers%20a%20rare%20chance%20to%20experience%20the%20authentic%20way%20of%20life%20of%20the%20Bonda%20people.%20Set%20in%20the%20beautiful%20Eastern%20Ghats%2C%20it%20is%20an%20unforgettable%20cultural%20experience.%20In%202025%2C%20the%20festival%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20celebrated%20on%2012%20February.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734147000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Flosar-1733406376.webp%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386842%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Beyond%20the%20snow%2C%20these%20hidden%20winter%20festivals%20shine%2C%20bringing%20together%20culture%2C%20faith%2C%20and%20the%20spirit%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20regions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386842%2Fwinter-festivals-india-tibetan-new-year-losar-magh-mela-himachal%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chef%E2%80%99s%20Choice%3A%207%20Must-Visit%20Spots%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20Best%20Samosas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20fast-changing%20landscape%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy%20has%20seen%20many%20recipes%20come%20and%20go.%20Some%20are%20fleeting%2C%20but%20then%20there%20are%20also%20the%20constants%2C%20embedded%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20social%20fabric.%20O