ish%20it%20loses%20its%20personality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChef%20Vikas%20Vibhuti%2C%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20memories%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346520%2Flist-of-iconic-food-places-peter-cat-tunday-kababi-paragon-amrik-sukhdev-mtr-karims-ram-ashraya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20iconic%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20associated%20with%20my%20OCLD%20(The%20Oberoi%20Centre%20of%20Learning%20and%20Development)%20days.%20It%20was%20a%20ritual%20every%20weekend%20to%20visit%20and%20enjoy%20butter%20chicken%20with%20%3Cem%3Echilli%20%3C%2Fem%3Egarlic%20%3Cem%3Enaan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20flatbread).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Mughal%20Mahal%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriter%20Marryam%20H%20Reshii%20calls%20the%20eatery%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20big%20daddy%20of%20butter%20chicken%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CCompetitors%20live%20in%20hope%20of%20uncovering%20some%20secret%20stash%20of%20canned%20Pelati%20tomatoes%20in%20their%20store%20room%2C%20but%20no%20luck%20so%20far%3A%20the%20sourness%20never%20varies!%20The%20progeny%20of%20Gulati%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%2C%20thanks%20to%20COVID%2C%20developed%20a%20brand%20called%20Yours%20Truly%20Butter%20Chicken%20with%20seven%20variants%20of%20the%20same%20theme!%20Yes%2C%20that%20is%20how%20fanatical%20we%20are%20about%20our%20national%20dish%2C%20hereabouts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20epicures%20have%20attempted%20to%20discover%20the%20secret%20behind%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20exquisite%20taste%2C%20some%20say%20it%20lies%20in%20the%20cream%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20come%20specially%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345649%2Fhistory-of-parsi-dairy-farm-mumbai-nariman-ardeshir-legacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dairy%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ashram%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20Delhi.%C2